"{\"uid\": \"myrepublica.nagariknetwork.com-news-asia-just-won-its-first-olympic-gold-in-a-sport-long-dominated-by-the-west\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Subscribe Now  PYONGYANG, Feb 16:\\u00a0Roared on by a home crowd, South Korea's Yun Sung-bin made history today.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 107, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 61, \"end\": 72, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9999999860815479, \"rank\": 7.243683804644958e-09, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 75, \"end\": 87, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yun_Sung-bin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yun Sung-bin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yun_Sung-bin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yun_Sung-bin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an event that until now had been dominated by Western athletes, he became the first Asian to win gold in skeleton at the Winter Olympics.\", \"from\": 108, \"to\": 248, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 195, \"end\": 200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999788774405, \"rank\": 1.547053896664693e-08, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, he became the first athlete outside of Europe or North America to medal at all in the sliding events-skeleton, luge, bobsleigh-at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 250, \"to\": 402, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What's more, he won with a comfortable margin, finishing 1.63 seconds ahead of the silver medalist Nikita Tregubov from Russia.\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 503, \"end\": 518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikita_Tregubov\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nikita Tregubov\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikita_Tregubov\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikita_Tregubov\"}, {\"begin\": 524, \"end\": 530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.8817348705797277, \"rank\": 0.13412774347055023, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nobody has won by such a wide margin in an Olympic sliding event in more than four decades.\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 623, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Britain's Dom Parsons took the bronze in the daredevil event, which involves barreling head first and belly down along an icy chute.\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 756, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 624, \"end\": 631, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9109434086779996, \"rank\": 0.09770758297816456, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 634, \"end\": 645, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dom_Parsons\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dom Parsons\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dom_Parsons\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dom_Parsons\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 23-year-old Yun earned the nickname \\\"Iron Man\\\" for his helmet, reminiscent of the comic book character's, and red racing suit.\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 888, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Pyeongchang 2018 Winter Olympics, men's skeleton gold medallist Yun Sung-bin of South Korea arrives at the finish area.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 1016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 961, \"end\": 973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yun_Sung-bin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\"